column2: Kinnikuman II Sei: Muscle Ninjin Soudatsu sen! Choujin Daisensou

In order to save a princess, Mantarou (Kid Muscle) and the gang must find a special ginseng. They are later joined by Kevin Mask. 

(Source: Wikipedia)
